<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 51" captionStartId="F51" captionText="Figure 51. Distribution of C. coccineum and C. cornutum." figureDoi="10.3897/phytokeys.200.71667.figure51" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/695466" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">51</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
